org.hkijena.jipipe.api

Class JIPipeProjectCacheQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.JIPipeProjectCacheQuery

  • public class JIPipeProjectCacheQuery
extends Object
    A query that allows to access a JIPipeProjectCache. This query caches the node cache states, so they are not always recalculated (which is expensive!)

        public JIPipeProjectCacheState getCachedId(JIPipeGraphNode node)
